snippet.textDisplay:
The opening instrumental sets the tone so perfectly. It rings like the beginning of a wedding celebration and also mirrors that passionate feeling of love that Anuv sings on <3

And although it starts out romantically, I feel it’s a special tribute to art and emotions. We’ve got thousands of musical gems out there, not made with unique words or phrases but still standing out because they’re a piece of someone's heart and mind
